International aid
Aid provided by the international community to Myanmar is now growing. The World Health Organization > has announced that it has activated its emergency management system and mobilization of its logistics center in Dubai to prepare supplies for the injured and spokesman Margaret Harris > has emphasized that it is coordinating its response to the earthquake from its headquarters in Geneva.
